# Optional local file: copy to `packages/alchemy/.env` (gitignored if you add it to .gitignore).
# Required for Alchemy CLI to reach Cloudflare (R2, Worker deploy).

# Preferred:
#   alchemy login

# Or set one of:
# CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
# CLOUDFLARE_API_KEY=
# CLOUDFLARE_EMAIL=

# Worker bindings are usually supplied by Alchemy from your app config + secrets;
# DATABASE_URL / BETTER_AUTH_* often mirror apps/server/.env — see docs/ENVIRONMENT.md
